=== 视觉字号（{{lang|en|Optical size}}）===

[[File:Unterschiedliche_Schriftformen_pro_Schriftgrösse.jpg|thumb]]
不同字号下的字形可能会为了让显示更清晰或个性更明显而有细微变化<ref name="MicroPlus">{{cite web|last1=Frere-Jones|first1=Tobias|title=MicroPlus|url=https://frerejones.com/blog/introducing-microplus|publisher=Frere-Jones Type|accessdate=1 December 2015|archive-date=2020-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409005839/https://frerejones.com/blog/introducing-microplus|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小尺寸的字形可能会优先考虑可读性，看起来更粗、更宽。大尺寸的字形因有足够的空间展示细节，可能会优先考虑设计风格，称为[[#特排字体|特排字体]]。这种设计差异继承自活字印刷的特殊处理。由于油墨在[[新闻纸|新闻纸]]印染时可能晕开，尤其是小尺寸可能会完全糊作一团，便要求对较小尺寸的活字作特殊处理，例如[[油墨擴張彌補|油墨擴張彌補]]。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reynolds & Koeberlin|title=Socialist TV Typeface Videtur Finally Freed|url=http://ilovetypography.com/2013/04/06/socialist-tv-typeface-videtur-finally-freed/|publisher=FontFont|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128103543/https://ilovetypography.com/2013/04/06/socialist-tv-typeface-videtur-finally-freed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

